      "title": "The price of imported samba rice and dal is reduced by Sathosa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The price of imported samba rice and red lentils sold in Sathosa outlets is Rs. 21 and 25 have been deducted. Accordingly, the new price of a kilo of imported samba rice is Rs. 194 and the price of a kilo of red lentils is Rs. 460."
      ],
